This comprehensive guide outlines best practices, conventions, and standards for development with modern web technologies including ReactJS, NextJS, React Native, Payload CMS, MongoDB, Redux, TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and Tailwindcss.

    Development Philosophy
    - Write clean, maintainable, and scalable code
